===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[pubic]] [[hair]]''' ''collective and singular, with plural'' '''pubic hairs'''

#(''collectively'') The hair that grows in the pubic region from [[puberty]]; the [[bush]].
#(''singular'') One of the individual hairs that grows in the pubic region.

====Synonyms====
*(''collectively''): [[bush]] (''slang''), [[short and curlies]] (''slang''), [[pubes]] (''slang'')
[[lady garden]] (''female slang'') - "I'm having my lady garden waxed at the weekend".
*(''singular''): [[pube]] (''slang'')

